h viele Unterschiede in der Globalisierung abgeschliffen haben. Trotzdem bleiben bemerkenswerte "Alleinstellungsmerkmale", die sich aber historisch gut plausibilisieren lassen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Jul 2018) 0aBusiness enterpriseszGermanyxHistoryy19th century. 0aBusiness enterpriseszGermanyxHistoryy20th century. 4aContemporary history. 4aEconomic history. 4aEconomics. 4aStructural transformation. 4aStrukturwandel. 4aWirtschaftsgeschichte. 4aZeitgeschichte. 4aÖkonomie.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2018z9783110603149oZDB-23-DEG0 cEPUBz97831103973900 cprintz978348658104140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783486841442423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783486841442.jpg  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017